Text: Days Left till Election DayDays Left till Election Day With just days left until Election Day we need your help to elect a probusiness Congress Each day there is news from highly contested targeted Congressional races Each week we will keep you informed about how you can help make sure business is victorious on November Today we need you to fill out an FEC required form to allow us to solicit contributions from you and your organization Please click here Electionsuschamberpachtm to fill out the form that will help elect a probusiness Congress Make a Difference for Business Tuesday November th is your day your day to vote your day to make your voice heard on the issues important to you your family your community and your country Please click on the following to find out how you can help get out the vote for business ElectionsGetOutTheVote Election FACT DOES YOUR VOTE COUNT YES and will make the difference in helping to elect probusiness candidates In Jon Fox won his congressional race in Pennsylvania by just a vote margin out of more than a quarter million cast In Sam Gejdenson won his congressional race in Connecticut by a margin of just votes In the presidential race John F Kennedy defeated Richard Nixon by twotenths of one percent of the vote That averages out to less than one vote per precinct nationwide Furthermore Kennedy would have been defeated if one more person in each of ten Cook County Illinois precincts had voted for Nixon To unsubscribe please reply to this email and type unsubscribe in the subject line
